#: ../../doc/docs/how_to/deploy/mrvl.rst:155
msgid "5. Compilation - Generating model partitions"
msgstr ""

#: ../../doc/docs/how_to/deploy/mrvl.rst:157
msgid ""
"In the TVMC mrvl flow, the model is partitioned into Marvell and LLVM "
"regions. Building each partitioned Marvell subgraph generates serialized "
"nodes.json and const.json. Partitioned nodes.json is the representation "
"of the model graph which is suitable for the Marvell mmlc compiler. It is"
" distributed separately via CDK"
msgstr ""

